<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>India's exports to China during the period amounted to1.56 billion dollars, up 29 per cent compared to corresponding period last year. China's exports to India from January to November touched 1.71 billion dollars, up 23 per cent when compared with the same period in 2000</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->. <br>
